  Scenario: Check Product Kit
    Given I go to Products/Products
    When I click view "sku_003" in grid
    Then I should see product with:
      | SKU              | sku_003                             |
      | Name             | Product Kit                         |
      | Type             | Kit                                 |
      | Product Family   | Default                             |
      | Is Featured      | No                                  |
